  "title": "In Marau-RS, several people sighted a two-pointed star with a tail [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/29/in-marau-rs-several-people-sighted-a-two-pointed-star-with-a-tail-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1eG",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 19th, 1996</strong>. Time: 20h30. Duration: not determined. In the city of Marau, state of Rio Grande do Sul, several people spotted an unidentified flying object in the western sector of the city. According to the witness who reported the case to COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command], the UFO looked like a &#8220;two-pointed star with a tail&#8221;. The sighting was observed with the naked eye by several people, with no reports of photographs taken or footage made of the sighting.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.418. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Marau, Estado do Rio Grande do Sul”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
